com.interpss.core.net

Interface Network<TBus extends Bus,TBranch extends Branch>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IChildNet, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AclfNetwork, AcscNetwork, BaseAclfNetwork<TBus,TBranch>, BaseAcscNetwork<TBus,TBranch>, BaseDStabNetwork<TBus,TBra>, DcNetwork, DistNetwork, DStabilityNetwork, OpfNetwork, PlanningAclfNetwork, PVDcNetwork, SENetwork, Static3PNetwork
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfNetworkImpl, AcscNetworkImpl, BaseAclfNetworkImpl, BaseAcscNetworkImpl, BaseDStabNetworkImpl, DcNetworkImpl, DistNetworkImpl, DStabilityNetworkImpl, NetworkImpl, OpfNetworkImpl, PlanningAclfNetworkImpl, PVDcNetworkImpl, SENetworkImpl, Static3PNetworkImpl

    public interface Network<TBus extends Bus,TBranch extends Branch>
extends NameTag, IChildNet
    A representation of the model object 'work'. The base network container class for storing buses and branches to format a power network.

    The following features are supported:

    • Time Stamp
    • Base Kva
    • Frequency
    • Bus Number Arranged
    • Data Checked
    • Bypass Data Check
    • Allow Ground Branch
    • Original Data Format
    • Ref Bus Type
    • Ref Bus Id Set
    • Area Map
    • Zone Map
    • Owner Map
    • Substation Map
    • Branch List
    • Bus List
    • Tie Line List
    • Extra Info
    • Child Net Wrapper List
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getNetwork()
